title: U.S. warns China over 'missiles' in S. China Sea
text:
U.S. warns China over 'missiles' in S. China Sea 11:31am BST - 02:06
The United States is warning China that there will be consequences for 'militarizing' the South China Sea. White House Spokeswoman Sarah Sanders made the remarks in response to a report that Beijing has moved missiles to the disputed Spratly Islands for the first time as Reuters' Gerry Doyle explains.
